%small
  #{books.offset_value + 1}〜#{books.offset_value + books.length }件
  \/ 全#{books.total_count.to_s(:delimited)}件
%table.ui.fixed.unstackable.table
  %thead
    %tr.computer.only
      %th.five.wide 作品名
      %th.four.wide 著者
      %th.four.wide 読了時間
      %th.two.wide 人気
      %th.five.wide.computer.only 書き出し

    %tr.mobile.only
      %th.six.wide
        %small 作品名
      %th.six.wide
        %small 著者
      %th.nine.wide
        %small 読了時間
        %small.right.floated 人気
  %tbody
    - if books.blank?
      %tr
        %td （作品がありません）
    - books.each do |book|
      %tr.computer.only
        %td
          = link_to author_category_book_path(author_id: book.author_id, category_id: book.category.id, id: book.id) do
            = book.title
            - if book.rights_reserved?
              %small
                %i.far.fa-copyright
        %td
          = link_to author_category_books_path(author_id: book.author_id, category_id: category.id) do
            = book.author.split(',').first
        %td
          = link_to author_category_books_path(author_id: author[:id], category_id: book.category.id) do
            = category_label(book.category)
          &nbsp;
          %small
            = book.words_count.to_s(:delimited)
            文字
        %td
          = access_count_stars(book.access_rating(:stars))
        %td
          %small= book.beginning.truncate(30)

      %tr.mobile.only.main
        %td
          = link_to author_category_book_path(author_id: book.author_id, category_id: book.category.id, id: book.id) do
            = book.title
            - if book.rights_reserved?
              %small
                %i.far.fa-copyright
        %td
          = link_to author_category_books_path(author_id: book.author_id, category_id: category.id) do
            = book.author.split(',').first
        %td
          = link_to author_category_books_path(author_id: author[:id], category_id: book.category.id) do
            = category_label(book.category)
          %small.right.floated= access_count_stars(book.access_rating(:stars))
      %tr.mobile.only.sub
        %td(colspan="3")
          %small= book.beginning

%small
  ※
  %i.far.fa-copyright
  マークのついた作品は著作権が存続しています。
  詳細は
  = link_to '青空文庫公式サイトの取り扱い基準', 'https://www.aozora.gr.jp/guide/kijyunn.html', target: :blank
  をご確認のうえ、取り扱いの際は十分注意してください。
